nodes.text: Morningfire was a male Jedi General that led Vornskr Company, a Grand Army of the Republic unit, during the Clone Wars. Vornskr Company was known to have operated in the Unknown Regions for at least part of the Clone Wars. General Morningfire and his company rescued the crew of a GAR vessel searching for Separatist supply depots after they were captured by the Near-Human natives of O'reen. The rescue was successful, but also ended in the death of O'reen's leader, the Magnus.

Morningfire was originally created by a player and developer of the Star Wars Roleplaying Game, and was canonized in The Unknown Regions, making this character one of the few fanon elements in continuity.
